The proof strategy is to use `funext` to prove the equality pointwise. Then, for an arbitrary point `v`, we need to show `proj_xy v + p.innerOffset = proj_xy (p.innerOffsetPart v)`.

This equality can be proven by simplifying both sides and showing they are equal. `proj_xy` applied to a vector `(x, y, z)` yields `(x, y, 0)`. `p.innerOffsetPart` applied to `v` yields `v + p.innerOffset`.

